short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Stackcrawler is a tool for checking tech stacks of websites.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stackcrawler technology profiler is a powerful tool designed to help developers, designers, and tech enthusiasts uncover the technology stacks behind any websites.

With just a few clicks, Stackcrawler provides detailed insights into the tools and technologies used to build and run any website.
